\r\ning it gratefully. True surrender\n is thinking of Lord with fascination and=\r\n pleasure, even in the face of (and during) Death.&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0&gt; &gt;&gt;If one with=\r\nout true surrender and with many desires and wrong notions experiences a Ku=\r\nndalini rise, one may still be trapped, despite thinking of a personal god.=\r\n It is not that god does not want to &quot;protect&quot; one as said below. It is not=\r\n about protecting or endangering. If you go back to my &quot;chipmunk glued to m=\r\nouse trap&quot; example above, I was trying to protect it, but it was scared. Si=\r\nmilarly, one&#39;s conditioning makes one *run away* from God&#39;s&gt; protection! Go=\r\nd&#39;s protection may seem to a conditioned mind like grave danger that one sh=\r\nould run away from!&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0&gt; &gt;&gt;*=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=\r\n=A0 *=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0 *&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0&gt; &gt;&gt;Whether thro=\r\nugh the path of wisdom or surrender, develop dispassion and detachment. Rea=\r\nlize that all this is temporary and can be taken away anytime. Enjoy it whi=\r\nle you have and keep doing your best, but be prepared to lose everything an=\r\nytime. Only detachment\n and a very light mental conditioning (very light de=\r\nsires, dislikes etc) can protect one as one&#39;s Kundalini rises to meet True =\r\nSelf. Heavy conditioning and impurities in one&#39;s nadis will distract rising=\r\n Kundalini (self-awareness) and stop Her from meeting True Self.&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0&gt;=\r\n &gt;&gt;The real key is how light your conditioning is.&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0&gt; &gt;&gt;Best regard=\r\ns,&gt; &gt;&gt;Narasimha&gt; &gt;&gt;--------&gt; &gt;&gt;Astrology & Spirituality Resources: http://w=\r\nww.vedicastrologer.org/&gt; &gt;&gt;--------&gt; &gt;&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;=C2=A0&gt; &gt;&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt;&gt;_____________=\r\n___________________&gt; &gt;&gt;&gt; From: Leela Sastry &gt; &gt;&gt;&gt;To: &quot;mailto:vedic-wis